eDescriptionTemporal:"Temporal mode prioritizes cards by time-based knowness development: cards that are old, unstable, or historically weaker are surfaced earlier, while strong recent cards are naturally deprioritized. The active queue is rebuilt to reduce forgetting risk and improve long-term retention rather than short-term completion speed. Use this mode when you want sustained maintenance of knowledge over days and weeks.",commonSettingsTitle:"Common settings",specificSettingsTitle:"Type-specific settings",settingsImpactTitle:"How this revision will behave",settingsImpactIntro:"These settings control card selection, order, and answer flow.",dependencyThresholdDisabledHint:"Enable dependencies to use this threshold.",effectCollection:"Cards are loaded from collection: {collection}.",effectTries:"Each card allows up to {value} self-attempt(s) before hint/reveal is shown; these extra attempts let you recover within the same card instead of being forced to move on immediately.",effectMinCorrectness:"Answers are accepted from {value}% correctness.",effectConsiderDependenciesOn:"Dependency checks are enabled: a card can be served only when its prerequisite cards (smaller knowledge units, required prior steps, or component fragments) are considered sufficiently learned. This enforces a foundation-first learning order and reduces failures caused by missing prerequisite context.",effectConsiderDependenciesOff:"Dependency checks are disabled; dependencies will not block cards.",effectDependencyThreshold:"A dependency is treated as satisfied at {value}% correctness.",effectStackSize:"The active queue keeps about {value} card(s).",effectLevels:"Cards can advance across {value} level(s).",effectCardsPerSession:"Each run draws up to {value} card(s) from the available pool.",effectReviewer:"Progress and knowness are saved for reviewer: {reviewer}.",levelsLabel:"Levels",stackLabel:"Stack size",levelsCurrentLabel:"Card level",levelsCountsLabel:"Cards per level",levelsStackLabel